1.	In Jenkins, create a Pipeline job.
2.	Write a Jenkinsfile in your GitHub repository.
3.	Configure pipeline script from SCM.
4.	Build the pipeline.
 in jenkins go to tools and iinstall maven 





jenkins file:
pipeline {
    agent any
    tools {
        maven 'M1'
    }
    stages {
        stage('Checkout') {
            steps {
                git branch: 'main', url: 'https://github.com/hawarya/devops_prac.git'
            }
        }
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean compile'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn test'
            }
        }
    }
}
